<sect1 id="dir_10cf350f37124dbdd00ea56cff4fe733_1autotoc_md49">
<title>helios::core::data</title><para>Core data primitives for identifiers, handles, and type indexing.</para>
<para>This module provides the foundational value types used across the engine for stable identification and efficient runtime lookups.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_10cf350f37124dbdd00ea56cff4fe733_1autotoc_md50">
<title>Key Types</title><para><table rows="4" cols="2"><row>
<entry thead="yes"><para>Type  </para>
</entry><entry thead="yes"><para>Purpose  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>StrongId&lt;Tag&gt;</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Tag-based, strongly-typed identifier with compile-time string hashing (FNV-1a)  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>RuntimeHandle&lt;StrongIdentifier, RuntimeId&gt;</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Lightweight pair of a stable <computeroutput>StrongId</computeroutput> and a dense runtime index  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>TypeIndexer</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Compile-time type-to-index mapping  </para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
</sect1>
